              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Opengrep Finding: go.lang.security.deserialization.unsafe-deserialization-interface.go-unsafe-deserialization-interface"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Deserializing into `interface{}` allows arbitrary data structures and types, which can lead to security vulnerabilities (CWE-502). Use a concrete struct type instead. Consider using github.com/ravisastryk/go-safeinput/safedeserialize for automatic protection."
